            <title>[LU-15865] don&apos;t report false eviction for lwp connections</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15865</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lightweight connections aren&apos;t persistent (i.e. not part of last_rcvd), so after target&apos;s restart such a connection is not restored, rather a new one created.&lt;br/&gt;
